{"tid":1030633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"江門買樓爛尾苦主請願　「投資大灣區血本無歸」","createTime":"2019-02-21T05:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T09:47:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":149,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"3f5fbab7b85597fcfae1e4dae7875ecb47ca4dc0","tid":1030633,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T05:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tsui_9wptI_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftsui_9wptI_1200x0.png&h=610b8adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京提出發展大灣區，近年亦興起在大灣區城市置業投資，約 30 名來自港、澳，在大灣區買樓投資最終爛尾的苦主，趁今早大灣區綱要宣講會到會長海洋公園萬豪酒店外請願，並在現場拉起「投資大灣區血本無歸」、「特首崔世安大力推薦」的標語，希望政府可以助他們討回血汗錢。<br />\n<br />\n到場請願的是江門地產項目「光博匯」的投資者，稱澳門特首崔世安曾大力推薦這項目，他們稱每人投資 50 萬元以上，買入光博匯住宅或商舖，但項目動工超過六年仍收樓，變成爛尾樓，估計整個項目的苦主多達 300 人，損失超過 7 億澳元，希望政府可以助他們討回血汗錢，更指對大灣區投資完全失去信心。警方派代表接收他們的請願信。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/宣講會-江門買樓爛尾苦主請願-投資大灣區血本無歸/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%AE%A3%E8%AC%9B%E6%9C%83-%E6%B1%9F%E9%96%80%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93%E7%88%9B%E5%B0%BE%E8%8B%A6%E4%B8%BB%E8%AB%8B%E9%A1%98-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%80%E6%9C%AC%E7%84%A1%E6%AD%B8%2F&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=ff1a1ced\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%AE%A3%E8%AC%9B%E6%9C%83-%E6%B1%9F%E9%96%80%E8%B2%B7%E6%A8%93%E7%88%9B%E5%B0%BE%E8%8B%A6%E4%B8%BB%E8%AB%8B%E9%A1%98-%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%80%E6%9C%AC%E7%84%A1%E6%AD%B8%2F&h=433bbf3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/宣講會-江門買樓爛尾苦主請願-投資大灣區血本無歸/</a>"},{"pid":"537030373c003396841193557aa4bb817ec3078b","tid":1030633,"uid":60092,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"大陸都好信, 抵死啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj